title: Me, Myself: A personal exploration journal
description: “Me, Myself” is a journal about you. It was designed to help you get to know who you are and what motivates you. Through a series of open-ended questions and writing prompts, “Me, Myself” will help you understand how to be the change that the world needs. It will also foster and spark your creativity, so that you better understand your dreams, fantasies and who you aspire to be.
author: Sharon Suniga
